additional_info: Ward Manufacturing Company of Greenville, Texas has been making fine quality pews for more than 50 years. As pew construction has changed over the past 30 years, Ward is one of very few companies that have retained features that add strength and durability to your pews. We offer more than the attractive appearance of Ward Pews. We refuse to compromise quality to lower initial costs. Instead, we choose to offer churches a pew with more solid wood, properly joined, resulting in more value for your money.
